==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: don't part even by a tiny step.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: cùn bù bù lí

===Idiom===
'''[[寸步]][[不]][[離]]'''

# to tag; to follow closely.

===Alternate forms===
[[寸步不离]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

